":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:48:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>買左,飛左4,5次成日都有d位差少少炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n室內飛？</blockquote><br />\n成日同d柱呀,電車纜擦身而過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飛埋d電車度好危險哦，d電線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試過一次以後唔敢,同埋試過飛飛下冇左圖傳signal,個gps又錯位,部mavic仲要已經飛到肉眼見唔到,嚇到我瀨屎咁"},{"pid":"1b085f2726305886a939c116f67cc0c8f2cdfc7a","tid":53792,"uid":21364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:22:15.000Z","msg":"買左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，之後可以飛得大膽d"},{"pid":"29e34a7c0f1843b13ba451b76e32d02fe64d8018","tid":53792,"uid":3931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T22:29:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>買左,飛左4,5次成日都有d位差少少炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n室內飛？</blockquote><br />\n成日同d柱呀,電車纜擦身而過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鐵同電纜影響signal 嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n教學有講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e412d16584a0882b6c93cdbae4b12e06390a33","tid":53792,"uid":2738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T00:47:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n成日同d柱呀,電車纜擦身而過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飛埋d電車度好危險哦，d電線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試過一次以後唔敢,同埋試過飛飛下冇左圖傳signal,個gps又錯位,部mavic仲要已經飛到肉眼見唔到,嚇到我瀨屎咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇signal之後點？會自己connect 返？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ac7d54ba9186a795ca8cb3641d2cec241006b5","tid":53792,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T00:59:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n成日同d柱呀,電車纜擦身而過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飛埋d電車度好危險哦，d電線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試過一次以後唔敢,同埋試過飛飛下冇左圖傳signal,個gps又錯位,部mavic仲要已經飛到肉眼見唔到,嚇到我瀨屎咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇signal之後點？會自己connect 返？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇圖傳signal基本差都依然可以控制到部機,不過係冇畫面睇,肉眼睇到部機既話咪手動控返自己身邊囉,肉睇唔到就要自動返航"},{"pid":"24fc3ab5293102b31fd431de37c3489f41d78708","tid":53792,"uid":2738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T01:02:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n試過一次以後唔敢,同埋試過飛飛下冇左圖傳signal,個gps又錯位,部mavic仲要已經飛到肉眼見唔到,嚇到我瀨屎咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇signal之後點？會自己connect 返？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇圖傳signal基本差都依然可以控制到部機,不過係冇畫面睇,肉眼睇到部機既話咪手動控返自己身邊囉,肉睇唔到就要自動返航</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自動返航識唔識避建築物咖？，定係會最短直線咁返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c70d0672a157f4d678376e9479fdec445f305c4c","tid":53792,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T01:14:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n試過一次以後唔敢,同埋試過飛飛下冇左圖傳signal,個gps又錯位,部mavic仲要已經飛到肉眼見唔到,嚇到我瀨屎咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇signal之後點？會自己connect 返？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇圖傳signal基本差都依然可以控制到部機,不過係冇畫面睇,肉眼睇到部機既話咪手動控返自己身邊囉,肉睇唔到就要自動返航</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自動返航識唔識避建築物咖？，定係會最短直線咁返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsuppose佢有前後左右同下面都有sensor識自動避,但我自己試過test下佢個sensor,覺得都唔係太可靠<br />\nbtw自動返航個陣可以控制佢高度,你驚既升夠2,300米左右囉,基本上都高過九成建築物"},{"pid":"ca24175a2b32f83396350dd8bc6acebb9d10cc38","tid":53792,"uid"